00:08:11.279 --> 00:08:16.880
value from a data visualization, or a graph, sorry, before it can be effective.

00:08:18.079 --> 00:08:24.079
So this is a very cliched thing to do, to show a slide with a quote on it.

00:08:25.679 --> 00:08:29.600
